Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter 1. The morning before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I woke before her like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The thin July light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,slipped through the half open
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,curtain,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and fell in a slanted stripe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,across Islander's bear shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed still,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,propped on my elbow, watching
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,her face as she slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A mouth slightly potted. Her
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,dark hair
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,spread across the pillow on my
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,side of the bed. One hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,curled near her chin like a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,child's.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The air conditioner hummed low
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,almost imperceptible, and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a scent of jasmine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,from the window. She'd insisted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,on planting jasmine on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the balcony, and I'd let it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.42,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,happen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,without arguing, which said a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.32,0:00:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,lot about what she'd done to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,me. There was a time when I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.34,0:00:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,sleep in that suite. Now it was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the opposite. I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't leave it without first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,making sure she was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,still there. I admitted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,inwardly, something I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,still felt embarrassed to say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,out loud. I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The words sounded strange in my
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,head. Almost indecent for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a man like me. Happy. I got up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled the sheet over her
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder so the AC wouldn't hit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,her
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,skin directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and went down barefoot. The cold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,marble of the staircase under my
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,feet was the same as always,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but even that seemed different
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,on the mornings she was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,upstairs. The mansions kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,at that hour was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,mine alone. Donakyara was still
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in the back garden cutting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,rosemary. I could hear from far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,off the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,sound of her scissors against
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the thick stems. The dogs slept
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,piled up near the service door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's old clock kept the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,slow rhythm of 620. I grabbed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the coffee tin,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,measured it into the mocha pot
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the way I landed her taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,without realizing she was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.23,0:01:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Two sugar cubes, a drop of milk,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,never two. Bastion came in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,through the service door with
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,his
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,planner under his arm, and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped talking before he even
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,started. He looked at me, looked
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,at the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,cup in my hand, looked back at
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,me. Good morning, he said dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, he said the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,planner on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,counter, with the ceremony of a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,man delivering an official
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,document. O second of silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Two ticks of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:01:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the clock. Should I build a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,household for the dawn becoming
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a barista? I didn't answer. The
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,corner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of my mouth betrayed half an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,intention of a smile, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,corrected it before he noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretended not to. That's how
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd worked for ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's on the schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fausto asked for half an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,this afternoon. The elders sent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,word about the dock, and Donak
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tavia. He paused, chose the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,word, requested a family meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,at noon. Formal sitting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at him. Did she request
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a meeting or announce one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Announced. I filed the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,information in the place where I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,store the things I haven't yet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,decided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what to do with. My mother had
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,come back from Naples two weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier than planned without
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,warning and without explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd expected her to arrive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with her temper sharpened,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,with a list of grievances, with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that silence of hers that cuts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,deeper than any shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't expected her to request
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the formal room. The formal room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,was for weddings, funerals,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and contract executions. By
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,mother knew very well what each
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,setting said before a single
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,word was spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Teller will be there. I'll ander
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I. Bastion nodded. Brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else? I raised the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this up before it gets
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,cold. Set it beside the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything. She hates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,being
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's not talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not talking to her. She's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,not talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not talking to her. She's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,not talking to her. She's not
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not talking to her. She's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,not talking to her. She's not
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not talking to her. She's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,not talking to her. She's not
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not talking to her. She's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,not talking to her. She's not
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,talking
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The flash from the neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,papers photographer had caught
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,her face at the exact moment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the bell told for the last time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and none of the guests knew how
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to look at her properly. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw in the photo the exact
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,moment her face understood that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Adelma wasn't coming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and I saw that she decided right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,there that she wouldn't cry in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,front of those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That day I decided two things
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm still keeping both to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,get her out of the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sarah Valls had set for her
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and to never tell her that I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,seen her cry in a white dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard light footsteps on the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs. The fourth step always
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,creaked and the sound reached me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the punctuality of an agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,upon signal. I came back to the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,present. I left the kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed the high ceiling to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor and passed through the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,hall to the garden. She'd be by
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,chamelears. She was always by
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the chamelears before eight said
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it was the hour when the flower
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is breathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She was, in a long night gown,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,hair pinned at the nape,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,watering can in her hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning still had that damp
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,July light that makes everything
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,seem slightly unreal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and she moved among the plants
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with the ease of someone born
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,there. Though I knew that three
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,months ago she barely knew the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,chamelears name. I came up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,behind her without a sound and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,kissed her
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,neck right where I'd learned she
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,shivers slightly. She shivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do that when I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you. If you soak the chamelears
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and me along with them, I won't
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,be offended. She laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,softly and turned her face until
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,she tucked her chin against my
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder. Her hair smelled of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,rosemary,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,probably because of Donna
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyara, who insisted on leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,dried sprigs in every room of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the house
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,as if that were protection
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,enough against anything. Your
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,mother is up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is always up to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,something. No. Today, she's up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to something. I looked at her
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,profile
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,against the morning light. She'd
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,learned to read the house the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,way one reads the Bible,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,word by word skipping nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If she said my mother was up to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,something, my mother was up to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,something. Formal sitting room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,noon, I said, we go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Together, it was just one word,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and it landed there like a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,signature at the bottom. I took
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the watering can from her hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,set it on the ground and pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,her to me by the waist. Beneath
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the cotton of the night gown,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a small secret only
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of us knew, and I could
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,count on my fingers the people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,outside that house who also
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,knew. Iolanda, me, the doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Donna Kiyara suspected, but
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Donna Kiyara
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,suspects everything and is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,rarely wrong. Do we tell them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,today? She asked against my
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother, your mother, I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,thought a second. After the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,meeting, we'll read the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,without speaking. I felt her
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,hair against my mouth and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,decided that this was the last
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,morning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd put anything off. After
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,lunch, I'd tell Fausto to pull
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the old contract out of the draw
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroy it with me in front
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of me at my signature. There was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a clause in it that I'd written
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with my own hand in another
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,life, and I'd carried the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,postponement of that clause, the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,way a man
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,carries a small stone in his
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,shoe, not annoying enough to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,make him stop, but always
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I was taking out the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,stone. Come, I said, eat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,something before you face the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,matriarch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She laughed again. She laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,more since she'd been mine. I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,learned to listen to her laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,way one learns a language he
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,never cared to learn and ended
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,up in love with its sound. We
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,went inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and the garden door closed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,behind us with the soft sound of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,old wood settling into its
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Four hours until noon, a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetime until noon. The formal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting room was the only room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion where I'd never felt
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,whole. Sealing too high,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,mahogany shelves with books no
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,one read,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,two sofas of dried blood-colored
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,velvet, and a rug so pale it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,felt cruel to step on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The air in there had that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,specific smell of a shut up room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you only open on occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Moth balls mixed with old
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,varnish, and something floral
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to mask the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Butavia liked that room because
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the room made an impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she chose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat with her back to the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,window, and the noon light came
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in behind her, and turned her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,into a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,dark silhouette against the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,gold, a staging choice, the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,choice of someone who knows how
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Bousto stood behind her, leaning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,against the shelves. His head
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,lowered in a way I'd never seen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the conceliary. Don Vittorio,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Emilliano, and Don Sisto
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,stood. The three of them with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that old
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,bearing of men who'd learned to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,stand for hours at wakes for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,friends they themselves had
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ordered
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,killed. I came in hand in hand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,with Ludovico. I felt his finger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,squeeze mine for half a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,almost involuntary, and let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He read the room before I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, son, Otevia moved her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,head
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a centimeter in my direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ealanda, I sat on the sofa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,across from them, him at my
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,side. I crossed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,my hands over my knee. There was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a dark leather folder on the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,little table between us, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,folder
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,was closed, and the folder had
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the crest of the lion with the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,broken crown blind embossed on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,cover. My stomach sank half an
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,inch. I recognized that crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same as the letter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,had arrived months ago. On a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,night when I still didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,understand much of what I was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The one Ludovico had put in the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,drawer without explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Otevia opened the folder with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:08:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,slowness of someone who knows no
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,one will interrupt. She took out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a sheet. Just one. Before my son
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,carries you twice. She said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,without looking at me yet, I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,thought it better you know the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,whole
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,contract. She pushed the sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,with two fingers to my edge of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the table. I didn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,moved half a second to late. I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,felt his hand hesitate on my
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,knee and settle there. I looked
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,at the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,sheet. It was paper yellowed at
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the edges. Family letterhead. My
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,signature at the bottom. That
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,shaky
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,signature I'd learned to make at
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the registry office months ago
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,with my head spinning from
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,hunger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and humiliation. And above my
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,signature, in the third clause
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,at the bottom, there was a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,paragraph
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,written by hand, by hand, not
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,typed, by hand. In the writing I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,knew from notes in the corners
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,library books, from messages
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,left at my bedroom door in the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,first month, from the dedication
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,written in a pavice novel and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,pretended hadn't been him. I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,read it once. On the day the air
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is born,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the marriage is dissolved. The
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,wife leaves with a fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,corresponding to half the dawn's
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,net worth, alone. Without the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,child, full custody remains with
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the Karachiolo family. I read it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The words didn't change. I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,raised my eyes to his profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He was looking at the sheet, not
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,at the sheet, and his mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,opened, and his mouth closed. He
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't say no. The tavia smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,without
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,smiling. Keep your word son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written in your own hand. I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,heard my own name sound inside
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,my head
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as if called from far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Iolanda. Iolanda, listen. That
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,writing is his. That paragraph
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That paragraph had been there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole time. Beneath
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,everything, while I learned his
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,while he pulled the sheet over
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,my shoulder, while we stood in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the garden with our hands inside
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,each others as if that were
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,real. He finally turned to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes were the exact color of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Himelia garden. And in that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,color, there was now a terror
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never seen on his face, not
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,in the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,small hours of the library, not
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,on the night of the attack in
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the street. Iolanda. No. I
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,stood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs answered. It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,mornings only luck. I smoothed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,my skirt with both hands as if
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,mattered. And I looked at the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,three elders, one by one, and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then atotavia. And lastly, very
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,lightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,at Ludovico. You two fit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,together. I said, the both of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you. My voice didn't shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To this day I don't know how. I
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,walked out of the room, though
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everything in me wanted to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My heels struck the marble of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the hall as if they belonged to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,another woman, and the other
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,woman
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,climbed the stairs far too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. One step, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the 13th
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to put my hand on the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,palm. I focused on that. Only on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that. In the bedroom corridor, I
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't go to the sweet I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,been sharing with him for three
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,months. I went to the door at
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the end. The door I hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:11:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,opened
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,since we'd decided to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,together. The white paint around
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the knob was slightly faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd noticed that detail on the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,first day, and completely
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten it afterward. The old
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,contract room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned the knob. The air
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.18,0:12:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,inside was still warm, with the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,smell of old wood, and the dust
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,gathers in places no one enters
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore. The bed made as on the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,day I'd left. The lamp on the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,night stand with its bulb off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The straw chair and the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,where I'd sat on the night of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking that was the worst that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,would ever happen to me. I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,closed the door behind me, and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the click of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the latch sounded loud through
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole house. I sat on the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,edge of the bed. The mattress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I laid my hand flat over the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,belly no one yet new existed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and for the first time in three
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,months,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I said quietly, to no one, and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to him, we're going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first lie I told my
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,child,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,chapter two, the closed door and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the man outside. The afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,fell over the old contract room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,without me moving from the edge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the bed. I watched the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,sunlight cross the floor in a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,long rectangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrink, stretch, shrink, vanish,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the room turned blue, then gray,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,then
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,black. I didn't turn on the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,light. There was a sound I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,learned to ignore over the past
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,months. The sound of the house
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,itself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing, pipes, wood
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,expanding. Donna kiaa's distant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps in the pantry. I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,listened to all of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it with a new attention, like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,someone arriving at a place for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time. The smell of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,cold wax
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,on the floor. The creek of a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,window at the end of the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor. The whole house
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,sounding like a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,living organism that didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was falling apart inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I started doing something I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't want to do and did
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway. I started rereading the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,last few
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,months backward, each gesture of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,his, and fitting them into the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,shape of that handwritten
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,paragraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The coffee, two cubes, a drop of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,milk. He'd noted it on the first
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Adbastion noted, kept the order
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,alive in the mansion's kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and at the cafe vekiae Roma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was the small
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,tenderness of a man who doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,know how to say the big things,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and what if it was just care of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,an investment? A man tens his
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,cattle with the same constancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but the same cold, calculated
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,attention, no affection, only
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,foresight. The coat over my
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders on the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,rainy night. I'd kept that coat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,at the back of the closet in the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,first week. The way one keeps a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The dark, heavy fabric, with his
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,scent mixed with the wet cold of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and what if it had been the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,calculation of a man who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,an elegant gesture buys cheap
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,loyalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The small hours of the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Him broken in the armchair. The
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,untouched glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about his dead brother. And
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what if every sentence of that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,had been rehearsed to soften a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,woman
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,who still thought she was
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,merchandise? And the handwritten
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,paragraph proved she was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I listened to that voice until I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,almost believed it. Then, I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,listened to another. The newer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The one three months old. The
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,one saying I wasn't an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an idiot. I'd seen his
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,face in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that room and I saw terror. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a game. I saw a man who didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,know what to do with his own
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,hands while
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,his mother slid the paper across
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the table. I stayed between the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,two voices until my mouth was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,dry to talk to myself. He
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,knocked on the door for the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,first time near nine at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Three short
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,knocks his way without pleading.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Alanda, I didn't answer. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,not coming in. I just want to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,know
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if you've eaten. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,answer. He stayed there. I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,his breathing on the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of the wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Held back, controlled. The way
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,he controlled everything. Except
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the things that truly mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard him let out the air like
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a man giving up on a sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,before saying it. I heard the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps drawing away far too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. As if he wanted to give
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,me time to change my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept dressed on top of the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,comforter. I dreamed of the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,church in Providence. In the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the bell wouldn't stop tolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I woke with the sun on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and my body heavy. I got up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,went to the adjoining bathroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,washed my face with cold water
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,until my cheeks stung. In the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the woman with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,swollen eyes and didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize her at first glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Second glance I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was still me, just more
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,tired. He knocked twice on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Friday. In the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in the voice of a man who
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,decided not to impose. In the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon, in a horse or voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the hours had scraped
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,something loose inside. Both
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,times he said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Both times I didn't open. Donna
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira came up with a train near
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,noon. She didn't knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She left the tray on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,against the door with a note
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,under the plate. I waited for
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,her footsteps to fade and opened
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the door the smallest crack. I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled the tray inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Soup, bread, a pair. The note
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,had three words in her round
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,motherly hand. Eat for the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew. Of course she knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Donna Kira knew everything in
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that house. I ate the whole bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,soup without tasting it. I ate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the bread. I ate the pair down
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to the core. It was the first
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,thing I did for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the little one. And the second
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,thing I did for myself. In Arena
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,called near five, I answered
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because it was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,her. Are you alive? I am. Are
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you eating? Now I am. You want
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,me to come over? I thought a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of having someone in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the room felt too big to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a strong light in an eye
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,used to the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,dark. Not today. Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow I'll say. She was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,silent long enough for me to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,know. She was thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,about not hanging up. And then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,she said her thing. If you need
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,wine and a butter knife,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you know where I live. I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed. It was half-laf,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,half-sob, but it was. It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,first time in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,24 hours that my face made a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,movement. It wasn't pain. I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,know. I answered. I hung up. Lay
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time I managed to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,without being angry at myself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for crying. I spent all of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Friday
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,outside that door. Not the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,time. There was a chair in the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor, a moss-coloured velvet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:17:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,armchair
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,one had used in years, and I sat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in it when my legs got tired of
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,standing. I came back to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,knock when I thought she might
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,hear. I never left the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion came up twice with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,office
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,questions and went down with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,short answers. Fausto asked to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,speak with me over the intercom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent word that not today. I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,leaned my forehead against the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,door's wood near the end of the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.38,0:18:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon, and spoke low without
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,calling her name. The wood was
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,cold. I let it stay that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.26,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote that before you existed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in my life. I stopped. Before I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,knew you'd exist in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped again. That doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,fix anything I know. On the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,other side her silence had wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell her silence is a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,part. There was her thoughtful
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,silence, her wounded silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,her sleeping silence. That was a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,new silence, a silence that was
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,weighing on me in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask to come in. I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't have the right. The
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,clause I'd written with my own
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in the week I decided to buy her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Sarah Valls, was the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,only piece of my history with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:18:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that she didn't know. And that's
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,why it was the only piece in
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,which she could still believe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,plan to lose her from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I forced that door now, I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't be opening a door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be confirming the paragraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I went back to the study at
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,eight. I called Bastion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You know this house. I do. Find
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,every copy of that contract. My
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,mother's Fausto's the one I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,peep in the safe. The one the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,registry sent to the secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,at a never came back. All of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring them to me. He stood still
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,half a second, enough to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,register that I wasn't asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And left without a single
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,question. I opened the drawer of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,my father's study and took out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,something that had sat there for
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,three months. The handwritten
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,draft of the clause.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yellowed paper, black ink, my
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,writing. I set it on the desk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and looked at it the way one
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,looks at
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a dead animal he hadn't the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,courage to bury when he should
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,have. There was a promise I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,made
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,my own conscience three months
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,ago. On the morning I Orlando
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,had agreed to sleep at my side
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,without
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a contract. I promised myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd erase that clause one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd put it off. I'd thought I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,have time. I'd put it off like a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,man putting off a doctor with
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,chest pain. And now the pain had
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,come for her not for me. And
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that was what truly hurt in the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,whole story. I put the draft
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,under the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,blotter. It wouldn't burn alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It would burn in front of the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,person who needed to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I went up again. I leaned my
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,forehead against the door one
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,last time that night. Good
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,night,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll under. On the other side, a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,second. Two. And a whisper so
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,low I could have invented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,night. I didn't invent it. She
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,said it. Saturday was born gray
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,with a pale light striking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,sideways
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,at the shutters and streaking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the floor with opaque bands. I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,got up before the heat pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Took a long bath, chose a light
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,dress, pinned my hair up with
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the two hands that no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,trembled so much. I opened the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,door of the old contract room
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and stepped out for the first
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,time in
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,almost 40 hours. I didn't go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for him. I knew that at
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,nine he'd be with Fausto in the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,downstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,office. I went down the opposite
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,side of the staircase and headed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to the winter garden where Dona
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiarra's brameleads caught the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,light through the glass and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,everything seemed quieter than
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of the house. Dona Kiarra
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared with a tray before I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,asked. Camo-Mail-T, a small
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,piece of bread
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,with butter, an orange peeled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,into segments. She set the tray
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,on the wicker table. Still to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dried her hands on her apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't look at me straight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,on. He loves you dear. She said,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at the bromeliads. Men
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,like him are stupid about the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,things they love. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't wait for an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.36,0:21:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,either. She went back inside. I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,drank the tea slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling the warmth of the cup in
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,my palms. I ate the whole piece
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of bread. I ate the orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I ate, I understood
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,something that had taken 40
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,hours to reach me. If he
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't tell it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd go after it. I'd done this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,before. Once ago I'd gone to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,find the truth about a delmo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with my own hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and the truth gave me back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,everything. Maybe the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,about that handwritten paragraph
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:21:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,was also
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,stored somewhere in the city, in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,an archive, in someone's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in his writing on some other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fausto probably knew. The cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Vecchia Roma, where everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,had begun, held the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And if there was a beginning, I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,still hadn't fully understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.16,0:22:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was mine. I took the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from my pocket and messageed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,bastion, car tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Early, just the two of us. He
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.37,0:22:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,answered
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in less than a minute. Yes, he
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't ask where to. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,warn the boss. Bastion was
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.94,0:22:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,bastion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent the rest of the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.62,0:22:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in the winter garden. Lutavico
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't come looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he knew I was there. On
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the other side of the glass. I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.99,0:22:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,knew he was waiting for a signal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,for me. And I knew he wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,force one. There was something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,new in that silence that I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,learned to read in the coming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,days, and that something was
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,respect. He was letting me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,choose the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of the afternoon I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,went up again. I passed the door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:22:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of his study. The door was a
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:22:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A threat of yellow light leaking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,through the gap. He was sitting
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.97,0:23:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,at the desk. No tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The shirt rolled to the elbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A pile of folders on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And a pile of folders on the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,left.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As if the work had come back to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,fill every hour I was away. He
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,was reading a sheet with an
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,attention that hurt to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He raised his eyes and saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't move. He didn't smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looked. The way he looked
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when he was holding something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,too big to fit into a sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night. I said, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all. I continued down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the corridor. I went to the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,suite that was hours and didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,go in. I went to the old
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,contract room. I laid dressed on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,comforter and on my belly,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.55,0:23:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,staring at the white ceiling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,until it stopped spinning. I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,closed my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was anyone who'd
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,learned to hunt her own truth in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the past months, it was me. To
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.58,0:23:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,borrow, I'd begin. Chapter 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What his handwriting never said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Day began cold. The way
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:23:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Providence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.86,0:23:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,knows how to be cold even in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.26,0:23:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,summer. The light came through
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the window of the old contract
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,room in
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,a hard way, without generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd slept little. My hand stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,open over my belly. The way it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,had already become habit these
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,past two days. And I wondered,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.61,0:24:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in the second before waking
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,fully,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.10,0:24:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,whether my child already knew
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.64,0:24:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that his mother had made a plan
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,with no one for a hunt. I got
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. Put on dark pants, a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.07,0:24:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,turtleneck, black shoes, nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.63,0:24:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that suggested Donna. Nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.28,0:24:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,suggested bride. Just a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.91,0:24:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with an address in her head and
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a question that would no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.39,0:24:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,fit
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.56,0:24:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,inside her. Bastion waited in
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.56,0:24:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the car, outside. He didn't ask
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.71,0:24:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a question. He just opened the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.78,0:24:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,rear door
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.40,0:24:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and kept looking straight ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.23,0:24:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,while I got in. The radio was
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.93,0:24:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,low, an old Italian song I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.76,0:24:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,without remembering from where.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.86,0:24:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cafe Vecchi Aroma, I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.61,0:24:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,buckling the belt, then the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.44,0:24:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,runnyeri office.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.04,0:24:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then an address I'll give you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.54,0:24:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,later. He nodded half a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.74,0:24:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,millimeter with his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.03,0:24:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Started the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.28,0:24:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The drive to the old
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.24,0:24:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,neighborhood took long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.63,0:25:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to count my breaths. We
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.06,0:25:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,passed the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.54,0:25:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,intersection where, months
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.98,0:25:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,before, a collector had shown up
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.74,0:25:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,at my apartment door with a
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.23,0:25:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Manila envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.06,0:25:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and a face that didn't ask
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.69,0:25:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,permission. I was another person
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.69,0:25:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that day. Or maybe I was the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.45,0:25:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,same,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.76,0:25:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,just not knowing yet. The dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.80,0:25:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,called three times. Bastion
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.64,0:25:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,said, watching the rear view
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.54,0:25:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.56,0:25:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice was always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.60,0:25:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Dry is dry stone. Asked where
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.56,0:25:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd gone. And you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.72,0:25:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that I didn't rightly know. I
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.60,0:25:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,smiled for a second. It didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.54,0:25:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,last. The cafe Vecchi Aroma sat
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.54,0:25:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,on a corner that time had
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.12,0:25:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten to renovate. Green
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.88,0:25:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,onning. Peeling sign. The smell
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.84,0:25:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of good coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.72,0:25:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,escaping through the door. I
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.54,0:25:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,went in slowly. Half a dozen
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.37,0:25:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,tables taken. Old men playing
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.26,0:25:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,cards in the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.04,0:25:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,back. A white-haired woman
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.78,0:25:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,reading a newspaper. I sat at
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.72,0:25:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the window table. The table. The
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.86,0:25:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,one where he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.80,0:25:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,sat on the late afternoon of a
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.54,0:25:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thursday that now seemed to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.11,0:25:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,belong to another life. His
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.68,0:25:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,chair was
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.20,0:25:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,empty across for me. And even
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.18,0:25:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,empty, it seemed occupied. The
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.22,0:26:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,waiter came slowly. He was a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.13,0:26:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,thin man,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.74,0:26:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,clean apron. With that look of
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.44,0:26:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who'd worked in an old
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.14,0:26:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,cafe since he was 15 and would
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.84,0:26:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,never
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.12,0:26:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,stop. Coffee, please. I said. He
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.30,0:26:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,paused half a second. Looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.40,0:26:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,me the way one checks a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.97,0:26:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,password.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.18,0:26:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Two cubes, a drop of milk. The
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.28,0:26:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,question landed between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.16,0:26:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet. I held my breath until it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.40,0:26:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,heard in my chest. How do you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.15,0:26:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,know? My voice came out lower
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.91,0:26:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,than I wanted. The waiter
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.42,0:26:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,shrugged
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.90,0:26:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with the kind of ease you only
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.04,0:26:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,learned with time. Old order.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.12,0:26:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Caracciolo asked a few
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.97,0:26:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,months back
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.76,0:26:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you ever came in, this
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.86,0:26:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,was how you were to be served.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.95,0:26:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Never came up. Today it did. He
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.12,0:26:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,left
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.40,0:26:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,before I could answer. I stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.05,0:26:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,staring at the wood of the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.44,0:26:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,table, breathing through my
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.88,0:26:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.54,0:26:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico had left a standing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.32,0:26:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,order at some ordinary cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.09,0:26:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Months ago. Without telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.06,0:26:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Without
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,asking for anything in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.23,0:26:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Without collecting. Like a man
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.96,0:26:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving a piece of home on every
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.80,0:26:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,corner of the city in case I
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.51,0:26:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,needed to come back. I really
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.27,0:27:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to be angry. Anger was
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.04,0:27:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,easier to carry. The coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.99,0:27:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,came. I drank it slowly. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.23,0:27:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly the way I liked it. And
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.46,0:27:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.68,0:27:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,taste came along with a new
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.49,0:27:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,scar. I paid. Left. Fausto
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.24,0:27:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranieri's office was on the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.05,0:27:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,second floor
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.86,0:27:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of a dark brick building. Three
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.92,0:27:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,blocks ahead. Bastion parked.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.84,0:27:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stayed in the car. I went up the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.96,0:27:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.36,0:27:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,alone. The wooden door had his
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.21,0:27:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,name and discreet gold letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.13,0:27:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of discretion that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.80,0:27:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,costs a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.04,0:27:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The secretary tried to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.78,0:27:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked straight past. With the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.58,0:27:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,politeness of someone who no
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.16,0:27:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,longer asks permission. Fausto
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.03,0:27:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,was behind the desk. Glasses at
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.97,0:27:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the tip of his nose. A paper
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.72,0:27:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,open in front of him. He raised
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.50,0:27:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,his head slowly when he saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.29,0:27:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't seem surprised. He
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.89,0:27:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.24,0:27:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,tired. He knew what I could at
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.36,0:27:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiolo. He said, Marcicano. I
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.41,0:27:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,corrected. Sitting in the chair
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.60,0:27:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other side of the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.52,0:27:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, he closed the paper
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.32,0:27:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. Crossed his hands. How
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.24,0:27:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.48,0:27:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When he wrote that clause.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.02,0:27:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fausto breathed through his
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.63,0:28:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,nose. Took off his glasses. Put
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.47,0:28:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,them in his
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.12,0:28:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,jacket pocket. Sinyora. I am the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.60,0:28:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,family's conciliate. My job is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.93,0:28:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to advise. Not to betray. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.18,0:28:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,not asking
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.96,0:28:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you to betray. I said without
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.07,0:28:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,raising my voice. I'm asking you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.40,0:28:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell me when. That's all. The
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.74,0:28:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,date.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.10,0:28:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He was silent for a while. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.99,0:28:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,he opened the drawer beneath the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.94,0:28:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,desk. Took out two bundles of
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.71,0:28:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,paper
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.02,0:28:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,tied within twine. Set the first
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.27,0:28:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of me and untied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.31,0:28:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Original draft. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.62,0:28:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,dated. By hand. You know the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.46,0:28:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,handwriting. I did. His writing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.51,0:28:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,was one of those you recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.48,0:28:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,from far off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.66,0:28:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,firm. A little old fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.61,0:28:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With the careful capitals of a
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.62,0:28:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,man educated by priests. The
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.50,0:28:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,date in the upper right corner
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.80,0:28:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,was a week before the day he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.10,0:28:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,called me to the cafe for the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.36,0:28:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.10,0:28:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A week before I existed in his
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.12,0:28:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,life in full. He drafted it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.94,0:28:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,alone. Fausto continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.22,0:28:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the sheet and not at
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.94,0:28:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,me. Locked in his father's
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.38,0:28:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,study. Didn't let me read it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.94,0:28:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,before I
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.38,0:29:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,witnessed the signature. Just
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.06,0:29:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,called me to certify the mark. I
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.92,0:29:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,asked if he was sure. He didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.71,0:29:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.72,0:29:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Fausto raised his eyes. He
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.75,0:29:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,had the kind of gaze a
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.19,0:29:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,conciliary learns. It doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.09,0:29:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.02,0:29:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't spare either. He
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.65,0:29:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't write this to bind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.23,0:29:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He wrote it to be sure he could
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.86,0:29:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,let
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.02,0:29:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you go. I gripped the edge of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.02,0:29:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the desk. The wood was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.95,0:29:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to hold. That doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.75,0:29:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,excuse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.62,0:29:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, low. It doesn't excuse
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.80,0:29:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it. Fausto tied the twine again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.13,0:29:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it away. It only explains
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.24,0:29:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.60,0:29:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed another minute. I had
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.58,0:29:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,no more questions. I stood. He
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.57,0:29:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,stood too in the polite way of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.55,0:29:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,old men.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.58,0:29:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Signora. He said when I was
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.37,0:29:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,already at the door. For
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.96,0:29:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever it's worth. He asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.09,0:29:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,three weeks ago
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.08,0:29:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to tear up that draft. I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.97,0:29:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd tear it. I didn't. I never
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.85,0:29:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,tear anything of the families
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.67,0:29:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,without a
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.24,0:29:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,written order. He knew I
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.61,0:29:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't tear it. And he went
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.27,0:29:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,away satisfied all the same. I
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.98,0:29:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped with my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.12,0:29:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,on the knob. I didn't turn
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.94,0:29:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,around. I just nodded and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.12,0:30:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Narina's apartment was in
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.87,0:30:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,federal
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.36,0:30:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,hill. Three streets below my old
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.30,0:30:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,one. Bastion parked at the curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.24,0:30:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Leant his head against the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.18,0:30:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Closed his eyes. I went up
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.92,0:30:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,alone. Rang the bell. She opened
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.05,0:30:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,wearing pajamas that must have
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.05,0:30:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,been
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.32,0:30:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,ten years old. Air pinned up
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.61,0:30:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with a pencil. Glasses crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.14,0:30:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God. She said,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.10,0:30:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,she pulled me inside by the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.61,0:30:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,elbow. You look like you saw
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.17,0:30:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ come down off the cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.48,0:30:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ feels like too little.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.19,0:30:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She closed the door with her
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.83,0:30:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,foot. Took me to the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.92,0:30:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shove to pile of sheet music to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.79,0:30:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the floor. Sat beside me. The
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.53,0:30:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment smelled of bad
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.98,0:30:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee and old books. And I,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.90,0:30:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,without meaning to, started to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.96,0:30:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,cry. It wasn't a pretty cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.30,0:30:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the cry of someone who'd
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.78,0:30:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,held it in for two days. Narina
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.27,0:30:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't say anything for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.22,0:30:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She just ran her hand over my
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.78,0:30:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,back. The way her grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.34,0:30:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,must have run her hand over her
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.00,0:30:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.22,0:30:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,child. Then she got up, went to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.03,0:30:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the kitchen, came back with a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.73,0:30:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,mug of bad coffee and a piece of
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.60,0:31:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,dry orange cake. Eat. She said,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.28,0:31:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,then talk. I ate. I talked. I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.79,0:31:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,told her about the folder,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.56,0:31:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the claws, his handwriting, the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.54,0:31:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,locked room, the cafe with the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.46,0:31:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,waiter and the two cubes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.66,0:31:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The draft in Faustos drawer. I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.28,0:31:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,told all of it in the messy way
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.96,0:31:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you tell your best friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.68,0:31:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,out of order, with repetition,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.57,0:31:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with a pause to breathe. I told
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.52,0:31:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,her about the belly. Narina
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.22,0:31:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.16,0:31:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the piece of cake fell into her
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.85,0:31:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,lap. She looked at me as if
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.32,0:31:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing me for the first time in
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.01,0:31:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.28,0:31:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,days. I, Alanda, I know she
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.51,0:31:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,cried. Then laughed. Then cried
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.06,0:31:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,again. Hugged me tight enough to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.70,0:31:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hurt my
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.28,0:31:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder. You're not fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.16,0:31:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,just for yourself, girl. She
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.97,0:31:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,said, still on my shoulder. This
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.04,0:31:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,changes the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.60,0:31:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I breathed deep inside her hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.69,0:31:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It really does change it. She
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.64,0:31:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,let me go. Wipe her face on
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.46,0:31:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.64,0:31:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,hand. That man wrote the claws
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.55,0:31:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because he was scared. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.33,0:31:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Said and done. Now either he
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.11,0:31:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,destroys
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.62,0:31:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the claws in front of his
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.88,0:32:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,mother-in-law, or I show up
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.25,0:32:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,there in person and he can deal
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.81,0:32:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with it. Choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.26,0:32:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed. It was a small laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.41,0:32:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was a laugh. We'll see. I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.56,0:32:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,said, she stood,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.12,0:32:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled me by the wrist. Before
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.60,0:32:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,anything you're going to the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.98,0:32:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.82,0:32:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurt. To the doctor, Alanda. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.09,0:32:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow. Today. You look like
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.23,0:32:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you haven't slept in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.50,0:32:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a little one in
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.90,0:32:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,there who needs a mother who's
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.45,0:32:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,whole. There was no arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.48,0:32:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nareena put shoes on me. Put a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.11,0:32:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,person in my hand. Pushed me out
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.84,0:32:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.46,0:32:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion lifted his head from the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.10,0:32:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,seat when he saw me. Looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.64,0:32:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nareena in the doorway. She came
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.28,0:32:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,down the stairs behind me. And
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.08,0:32:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,at a mug of coffee to bastion
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.82,0:32:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,through the car window. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.74,0:32:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.02,0:32:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's hot. Bastion accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.72,0:32:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it with that minimal nod of the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.47,0:32:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,head. Nareena waited for me to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.17,0:32:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,get in the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.74,0:32:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,car. Patted the hood twice like
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.70,0:32:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,someone saying goodbye to a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.41,0:32:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,horse. Went back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.12,0:32:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastion looked at the mug for
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.71,0:32:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,half a second before taking the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.41,0:32:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,first sip. Miss Nareena. He
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.89,0:32:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,said,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.50,0:33:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,low, more to himself than to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.69,0:33:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Has a heavy hand. With the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.48,0:33:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee or with life. Both. He
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.46,0:33:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,started the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.06,0:33:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The family's discreet clinic was
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.71,0:33:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in a building with no sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.10,0:33:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Three floors above a jewelry
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.54,0:33:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,shop on
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.90,0:33:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,a quiet street. I went up in the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.79,0:33:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,elevator with Bastion behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.68,0:33:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A silent shadow. The doctor was
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.51,0:33:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.92,0:33:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of around 50. Short gray hair. A
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.07,0:33:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,firm hand. She'd already treated
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.22,0:33:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,two generations of Karachi
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.96,0:33:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Olos. She examined me carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.99,0:33:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask questions without going
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.69,0:33:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,around anything. Marked
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.15,0:33:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,something
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.72,0:33:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in a chart I didn't see. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.29,0:33:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,she sat in the chair across from
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.03,0:33:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,me and crossed her hands. The
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.60,0:33:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,way
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.76,0:33:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fausto had crossed his hours
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.16,0:33:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier. It must be a habit of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.65,0:33:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,those who live around this
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.95,0:33:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,family.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.80,0:33:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's fine with the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.24,0:33:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,child. She said, but your blood
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.97,0:33:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,pressure is high. Higher than
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.58,0:33:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.02,0:33:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,this stage. You need rest. You
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.85,0:33:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,need to sleep. And above all you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.81,0:33:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,need to avoid any big shocks in
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.71,0:33:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the coming
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.32,0:33:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,months. A big shock drops the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.24,0:33:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,pressure. Dropped pressure drops
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.35,0:33:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the child. I laughed awkwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.88,0:33:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the kind of laugh that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.18,0:33:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't a laugh. The one that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.38,0:34:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,comes out of your chest because
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.77,0:34:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,there's
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.08,0:34:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,nowhere else for it to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.28,0:34:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I said, I've had three
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.34,0:34:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,big shocks in the last 72 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.94,0:34:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't smile. She just
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.54,0:34:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,gripped the pen in her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.27,0:34:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then avoid the room. She gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.24,0:34:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,vitamins.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.02,0:34:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A prescription. A sheet with
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.85,0:34:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,emergency numbers. Bastion paid
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.88,0:34:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,downstairs with an envelope that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.98,0:34:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared from his coat pocket as
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.77,0:34:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,if it had always been there. We
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.49,0:34:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,went back to the car. After noon
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.28,0:34:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,had already fallen. Home, I
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.22,0:34:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,said, Bastion nodded. The drive
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.45,0:34:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,back was long the way roads get
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.67,0:34:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,long
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.96,0:34:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when your head is full. I looked
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.82,0:34:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,at the street without seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.67,0:34:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I went over everything. The
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.24,0:34:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,date in the corner of the draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.15,0:34:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fausto's sentence. Narina's
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.75,0:34:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,gesture holding the piece of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.42,0:34:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,cake in
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.84,0:34:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,her lap. The doctor gripping the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.27,0:34:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,pen. And in the middle of it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.39,0:34:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,all, something new. I wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.52,0:34:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,just
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.82,0:34:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,wounded anymore. I was planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.75,0:34:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We reached the mansion when it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.55,0:34:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,was already night. Bastion
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.12,0:34:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.54,0:34:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the car in the courtyard. Got
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.29,0:34:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,out. Open the door for me. I
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.97,0:35:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,climbed the three entrance steps
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.90,0:35:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.92,0:35:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The front door opened before I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.57,0:35:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,touched it. Ludovico was at the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.28,0:35:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,foot of the stairs. Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.76,0:35:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,where
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.04,0:35:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd waited. Months ago, when
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.76,0:35:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd tried to leave alone for the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.65,0:35:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,first time and Renolfo had shown
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.54,0:35:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,up in the street behind the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.31,0:35:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,market. The same place. The same
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.40,0:35:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,height. His hands at his sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.43,0:35:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.28,0:35:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,straight. His mouth closed in a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.21,0:35:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,line that couldn't hide that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.96,0:35:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd waited there for hours. I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.82,0:35:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.26,0:35:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of the hall. The
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.17,0:35:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,marble floor gave back the echo
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.14,0:35:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of my heels. Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.05,0:35:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.86,0:35:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't a question. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.35,0:35:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,just his voice trying to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.95,0:35:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the edge of something. I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.23,0:35:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.76,0:35:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the place. I recognized the foot
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.58,0:35:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of the stairs and the waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.29,0:35:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I let the recognition pass
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.00,0:35:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,across
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.34,0:35:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,my face without hiding it. After
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.46,0:35:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you, I said, except you weren't
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.50,0:35:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,there. He closed his eyes half a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.62,0:35:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,second. Open them. I'll land a.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.79,0:35:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will talk. I passed him
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.03,0:35:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,without touching. Climb the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.92,0:35:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.34,0:35:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. One hand on my belly
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.10,0:35:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,under the coat, the other on the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.10,0:36:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,railing. He didn't follow. He
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.92,0:36:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.30,0:36:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,where he was. The way men stay
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.04,0:36:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,when they've learned too late
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.72,0:36:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that grabbing doesn't hold. I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.41,0:36:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,lay
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.58,0:36:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,down in the old contract room.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.75,0:36:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The bed was still cold, but I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.84,0:36:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,slept. Not much, but I slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.46,0:36:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the small hours that woke
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.41,0:36:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,me. A muffled sound. Downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.37,0:36:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind the mansion shouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.20,0:36:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,make at that hour. I sat up on
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.15,0:36:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the bed with my eyes closed for
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.15,0:36:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a second. Tuning my ear. Light
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.10,0:36:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps in the downstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.07,0:36:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor. A door opening slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.41,0:36:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And a voice. A table. On the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.46,0:36:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.90,0:36:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking Italian too fast. The
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.81,0:36:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,way someone does when they don't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.86,0:36:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,want to be understood. I got up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.20,0:36:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressed my ear to the crack of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.71,0:36:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the door frame. The mansion's
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.18,0:36:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,high ceilings carried sound
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.54,0:36:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,upward
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.84,0:36:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,as if designed for it. And I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.69,0:36:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,caught three words in the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.34,0:36:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,current of hers. Enough. Air.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.88,0:36:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarah Vall. I stayed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.61,0:36:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressed against the wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.21,0:36:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Without breathing. My hand went
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.20,0:36:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,back to my
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.84,0:36:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,belly without me telling it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.76,0:36:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I understood. Without
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.26,0:37:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,needing another word. That the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.06,0:37:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,witch
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.36,0:37:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't scheming alone. She'd
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.80,0:37:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,arranged the next step with the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.40,0:37:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,enemy Ludovico thought was
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.74,0:37:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.78,0:37:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I went back to bed slowly. I
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.59,0:37:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't lie down. I sat leaning
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.53,0:37:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,against the headboard. I's open
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.53,0:37:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.92,0:37:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,dark. Waiting for dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.37,0:37:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow. Ludovico was going to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.31,0:37:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,hear me out tomorrow. I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.07,0:37:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.46,0:37:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd been in the library since
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.83,0:37:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,before dawn. The way I always
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.19,0:37:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,had been when the house demanded
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.70,0:37:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,something I didn't yet know how
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.73,0:37:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to give. A low fire in the half.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.82,0:37:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The coal eating itself slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.72,0:37:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,from within. With that dry
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.29,0:37:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,crackle that filled the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.16,0:37:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,without truly filling it. An
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.86,0:37:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,untouched
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.40,0:37:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,glass beside the arm of the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.87,0:37:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,chair. The glass of a man who
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.44,0:37:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,pours out of habit and doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.07,0:37:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.80,0:37:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning light still had that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.55,0:37:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,grey tone of the small hours
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.08,0:37:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that hasn't decided between
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.56,0:37:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,dark and day. And I waited
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.22,0:37:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,without waiting. My eyes fixed
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.13,0:37:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,on the embers. As if they might
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.11,0:37:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.56,0:37:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,something I still didn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.50,0:37:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the courage to tell myself. I
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.45,0:37:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,heard her step on the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.32,0:37:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,before I
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.86,0:37:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized it by the weight. The
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.60,0:38:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,heels she wore inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.33,0:38:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Later than the ones for the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.80,0:38:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,street.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.80,0:38:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A second slower than usual
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.51,0:38:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because her body now carried a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.48,0:38:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,secret that tired her more than
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.52,0:38:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,she
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.72,0:38:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,admitted. She came in through
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.39,0:38:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the library's arch door and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.94,0:38:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped half a second at the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.55,0:38:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.20,0:38:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hand still on the wooden
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.02,0:38:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,frame. She was in a loose
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.64,0:38:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,blouse. Her pinned up. No
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.26,0:38:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,make-up. I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.04,0:38:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,never seen her like this in the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.69,0:38:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,morning. Even with anger written
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.39,0:38:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,into every muscle of her face,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.98,0:38:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,she was the most alive thing in
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.76,0:38:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that room full of dead books.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.42,0:38:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked at the empty arm
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.97,0:38:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,chair
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.26,0:38:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,beside me. Mine. She sat in it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.24,0:38:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway, with that deliberate
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.09,0:38:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,calm of someone who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.74,0:38:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.20,0:38:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what she's doing and wants you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.00,0:38:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to see. She crossed her legs
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.68,0:38:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. She held my gaze without
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.60,0:38:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,blinking. Explain it to me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.76,0:38:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,she said. Without cutting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.50,0:38:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,anything out. I breathed deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.59,0:38:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The air
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.08,0:38:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,was warm near the hearth and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.77,0:38:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,cold on the opposite side, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.70,0:38:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,felt both at the same time. If
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.52,0:38:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there's
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.94,0:38:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,something I've learned about
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.35,0:38:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,speaking, I've learned that the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.92,0:38:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,truth only fits in your mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.38,0:39:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when you accept losing something
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.26,0:39:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,by saying it. I'd accepted it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.96,0:39:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,since Friday morning. When I
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.60,0:39:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,leaned my forehead against the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.92,0:39:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,door of the room where she was
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.24,0:39:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,locked and admitted to the word
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.60,0:39:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that the clause was mine and the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.46,0:39:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,price of it was too. The first
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.21,0:39:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,time I wanted to tell you this
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.96,0:39:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,story I began was in the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.51,0:39:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen. He lifted her chin half
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.59,0:39:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a millimeter. She knew which
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.40,0:39:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.92,0:39:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd been in the house a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.68,0:39:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I continued. I'd agreed with
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.28,0:39:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,myself that I wouldn't speak to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.04,0:39:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you in the corridors. Formal
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.58,0:39:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting cold-look public dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.33,0:39:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,contract, that was the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.54,0:39:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.82,0:39:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You cried in the small hours
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.32,0:39:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,alone at the counter and the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.82,0:39:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,light you'd left on made me come
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.53,0:39:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.20,0:39:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to leave without
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.95,0:39:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,going in. You heard me, turned
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.83,0:39:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,around, and fired off a sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.84,0:39:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.90,0:39:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,still hear when I have nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.66,0:39:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to do. She stayed quiet. Her
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.31,0:39:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,hands rested in her lap,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.72,0:39:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with a stillness I recognized as
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.76,0:39:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,effort. I don't need an audience
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.79,0:39:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to cry, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.08,0:39:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeated it without trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.74,0:39:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,imitate her. No one had ever
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.25,0:39:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,spoken to me like that. Not a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.81,0:39:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,man,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.24,0:39:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,not a woman, not my father. In
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.77,0:39:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that moment I understood two
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.20,0:40:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,things I didn't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.38,0:40:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.42,0:40:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The first, that you wouldn't fit
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.19,0:40:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,into the contract I'd written,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.86,0:40:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the second that I was going to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.52,0:40:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.14,0:40:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I fell right there. That
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.19,0:40:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,night, with the glass of milk,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.38,0:40:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,still in your hand. She pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.64,0:40:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.86,0:40:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,pack of the armchair with her
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.44,0:40:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,fingertips. She didn't interrupt
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.18,0:40:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,me. The second time was in the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.81,0:40:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.40,0:40:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I continued. Coming back from
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.27,0:40:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Miljira Soli, you got into the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.20,0:40:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,car beside me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.30,0:40:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,wet from the shoulder up, your
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.88,0:40:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,hair stuck to your neck. I took
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.52,0:40:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,off my coat before I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.00,0:40:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and covered you. I was without a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.45,0:40:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,coat the rest of the way the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.72,0:40:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,cold coming in through the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.90,0:40:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,window.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.64,0:40:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What I didn't tell you is that I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.53,0:40:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,got home not trusting my own
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.19,0:40:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,voice. I didn't open my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.90,0:40:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,until the sweet door. If I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.58,0:40:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,spoken, I'd have said something
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.44,0:40:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that couldn't yet be said,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.24,0:40:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and the clause, the voice came
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.99,0:40:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,quiet. But with a firmness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.50,0:40:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,underneath that left no room for
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.36,0:40:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.42,0:40:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,vision. When, there I closed my
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.65,0:40:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes a second. The cold popped
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.82,0:40:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,softly in the hearth. I opened
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.98,0:40:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.50,0:40:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In the week I discovered the set
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.31,0:41:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of Alice Plan, I said, before I
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.06,0:41:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,called you to the cafe,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.82,0:41:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was alone in my father's
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.26,0:41:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,study. I'd already decided to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.86,0:41:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,buy the debt. I'd already
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.25,0:41:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,decided to get
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.02,0:41:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Delmo out of the city. I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.63,0:41:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,already decided on the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.60,0:41:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I drafted it all by hand at
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.52,0:41:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that mahogany writing desk with
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.44,0:41:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the window facing the winter
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.18,0:41:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,garden, each line in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.42,0:41:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The only sound, the scratch of
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.37,0:41:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the pen on paper. She didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.19,0:41:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,look away. The final clause I
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.08,0:41:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,wrote last, I continued. After
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.17,0:41:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,everything, Fausto wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.41,0:41:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was. I wrote it because
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.50,0:41:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,if one day you found out who I
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.07,0:41:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,really was and were left with no
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.75,0:41:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,choice, I wanted you to be
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.12,0:41:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,able to leave. Without having to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.94,0:41:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,ask, without having to knock on
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.70,0:41:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,my door asking permission to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.90,0:41:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,with money to start over in
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.30,0:41:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever city you wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.60,0:41:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,without my name on your passport
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.27,0:41:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,if you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.58,0:41:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,preferred it that way. Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.52,0:41:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A log tapped lightly against the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.53,0:41:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,iron grate of the hearth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.44,0:41:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I alander, I said, and my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.28,0:41:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,was no longer firm. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.94,0:41:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,know how to love without leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.84,0:41:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a door
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.20,0:41:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,open. Writing that clause was
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.84,0:42:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the only form of love I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.25,0:42:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,learned, building the exit for
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.94,0:42:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,someone
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.34,0:42:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think would stay. She
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.33,0:42:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,breathed deep. Her chest rose
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.26,0:42:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and fell in a way I noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.60,0:42:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hated myself for noticing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.54,0:42:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so clearly. Chapter 4. The
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.16,0:42:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,writing on the page, the voice
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.03,0:42:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in the ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.72,0:42:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And afterward, she said, it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.58,0:42:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't a question. It was an
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.52,0:42:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,order. Afterward, I loved you. I
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.72,0:42:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,said
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.00,0:42:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,simply. And I put it off. I
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.71,0:42:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,thought I'd have time. I asked
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.61,0:42:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fausto to tear up the draft
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.33,0:42:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.34,0:42:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd tear it. I knew he
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.03,0:42:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't tear it because a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.45,0:42:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,conciliary doesn't tear paper
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.03,0:42:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,without a
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.52,0:42:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,written order. I came away
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.11,0:42:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,without demanding the written
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.89,0:42:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,order. Because inside, I still
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.73,0:42:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.40,0:42:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if I deserved to destroy the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.92,0:42:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,door. She said nothing more for
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.61,0:42:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a while. The silence between us
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.30,0:42:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,had
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.46,0:42:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,its own weight and temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.20,0:42:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then she stood. She walked to
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.82,0:42:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the hearth with measured steps,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.08,0:42:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,as if she needed something
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.56,0:42:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,concrete to look at. She stood
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.26,0:42:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,with her back to me, facing the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.02,0:42:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.30,0:42:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Her shoulders were slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.85,0:42:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,slumped. The way someone carries
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.69,0:42:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,an invisible baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.12,0:43:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and too heavy a truth on the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.71,0:43:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,same day. The reddish light of
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.41,0:43:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the embers struck her profile
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.05,0:43:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.62,0:43:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there. Quiet. Long enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.60,0:43:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to realize she was using that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.40,0:43:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,silence to organize something
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.20,0:43:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,within herself. You put it off,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.87,0:43:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,she said, without turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.27,0:43:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's different from lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.28,0:43:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It is. I said, low. But it costs
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.65,0:43:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the same. She turned. Her eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.88,0:43:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,were red. But they didn't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.18,0:43:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't forgive you today, she
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.80,0:43:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,said. But I understand for today
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.54,0:43:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's what I can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.28,0:43:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood from the armchair
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.01,0:43:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. I didn't approach. I
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.94,0:43:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,learned late, but I learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.87,0:43:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.64,0:43:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I said. She nodded half a
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.06,0:43:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,millimeter with her head. She
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.71,0:43:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,passed me without touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.92,0:43:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stopped at the doorframe her
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.21,0:43:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,hand in the same place where
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.50,0:43:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd stopped coming in,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.84,0:43:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the frame were a border
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.44,0:43:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,she controlled alone. There's
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.04,0:43:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,another thing, she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.36,0:43:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll tell you later, not
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.06,0:43:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,today, she left. I stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.57,0:43:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at the fire, the glass
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.39,0:43:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,remained
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.88,0:43:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,untouched. I left the library
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.97,0:43:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,without running. If I ran, he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.20,0:44:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,come after me. And I still
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.07,0:44:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.50,0:44:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,decided what to do with what was
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.17,0:44:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,inside me in that minute. The
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.69,0:44:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,anger that still burned and that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.36,0:44:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,other thing deeper than anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.03,0:44:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that hurt in a different
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.80,0:44:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,way because it had no easy name.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.94,0:44:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked down the corridor to
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.46,0:44:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,his father's old study. The wood
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.14,0:44:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of the floor was cold under my
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.72,0:44:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,heels. The smell of Carnoboax
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.73,0:44:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and old paper marking each step.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.96,0:44:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico had shown me the key
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.97,0:44:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,once,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.64,0:44:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,months before. In the casual way
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.74,0:44:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of a man saying, this door is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.63,0:44:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,yours too. I'd never gone in
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.47,0:44:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.34,0:44:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I went in now. The study was
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.17,0:44:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,darker than Ludovico's. Heavy or
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.27,0:44:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,wood. The thick wool rug with a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.30,0:44:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,burgundy diamond pattern that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.84,0:44:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,muffled any sound. The smell of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.48,0:44:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,old cigar that never fully left
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.12,0:44:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.28,0:44:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,walls no matter how they opened
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.95,0:44:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the window. The writing desk sat
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.67,0:44:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle, facing the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.02,0:44:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,closed window. I went straight
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.63,0:44:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to the top drawer without
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.98,0:44:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,hesitating. Like someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.48,0:44:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,knows what
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.02,0:44:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,she came to get. It wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.68,0:44:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,locked. He trusted the people
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.52,0:44:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,living with him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.11,0:44:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.94,0:44:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,among folders and sealed
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.22,0:44:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,envelopes, I didn't even dare
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.76,0:45:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,touch. An old leather notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.36,0:45:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with a crumpled
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.16,0:45:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,corner. I opened it. Loose
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.93,0:45:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,sheets of drafts, some with
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.77,0:45:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,incorrections, and others with
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.82,0:45:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,edges
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.16,0:45:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,yellowed by time. I found it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.71,0:45:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,without needing to search much.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.43,0:45:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The handwriting was
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.48,0:45:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.20,0:45:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The same one I'd already learned
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.93,0:45:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to recognize in every note and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.55,0:45:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,dedication in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.32,0:45:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Date in the upper right corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.41,0:45:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A week before the day of the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.30,0:45:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,cafe. It was all there. All by
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.32,0:45:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.10,0:45:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with each clause numbered and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.50,0:45:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the last one written on the back
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.04,0:45:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sheet. Separated from the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.58,0:45:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,others by a simple horizontal
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.07,0:45:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,line. I folded the sheet in four
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.71,0:45:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with the care of someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.14,0:45:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,knows
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.40,0:45:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,old paper tears. I put it in the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.46,0:45:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,pocket of my dress. At my hip. I
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.53,0:45:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,closed the drawer slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.14,0:45:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,with two fingers, without a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.23,0:45:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,sound. I left. In the upstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.56,0:45:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,corridor I stopped. Otevia's
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.73,0:45:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,voice rose
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.50,0:45:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,through the stairwell, with the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.14,0:45:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,clarity that only the mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.67,0:45:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,knew how to give. The ceiling
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.20,0:45:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,was
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.36,0:45:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely high in that stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.04,0:45:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And the salon of the formal
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.51,0:45:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting room sat right below my
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.19,0:45:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.90,0:45:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The same room where she'd opened
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.44,0:45:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the folder three days before.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.83,0:46:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With that smile of someone who'd
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.37,0:46:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,kept
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.56,0:46:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the card up her sleeve her whole
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.37,0:46:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,life. The salon door was a jar,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.13,0:46:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sound rose through the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.83,0:46:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,gap,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.06,0:46:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as if someone had planted an
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.70,0:46:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,acoustic pipe between the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.17,0:46:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,floors. She wasn't speaking low.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.05,0:46:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She never
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.58,0:46:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,spoke low when she thought only
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.27,0:46:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,elders were listening. I leaned
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.96,0:46:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,my hand on the railing. The iron
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.70,0:46:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,cold against my palm. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.69,0:46:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,crouch. I just stood. My son has
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.80,0:46:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped listening to the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.40,0:46:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She was saying. Bastetalion
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.83,0:46:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,mixed with English. The
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.05,0:46:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,syllables cutting the air with
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.63,0:46:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the precision of
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.48,0:46:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who'd practiced that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.95,0:46:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,speech before. He let the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.58,0:46:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,nurse his decision. And the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.00,0:46:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,three of
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.42,0:46:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,stakequia as if the Donna hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.13,0:46:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,been chosen in this room for
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.63,0:46:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,three generations. A male voice
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.29,0:46:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,answered
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.72,0:46:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,low. Don Vittorio by the grave
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.70,0:46:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,deliberate timbre. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.48,0:46:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,catch the words. Don't come to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.46,0:46:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,me with
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.92,0:46:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a Tavia. She cut in. You signed
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.06,0:46:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the original contract with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.13,0:46:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The clause exists. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.72,0:46:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.10,0:46:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to enforce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.37,0:46:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Another answer. Also low. Also
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.81,0:47:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,his. It only takes one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.16,0:47:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Matevia said. And their her
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.12,0:47:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,voice changed tone. Ruth inner.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.37,0:47:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharper. That quality of a knife
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.69,0:47:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,passing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.20,0:47:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,over a wetstone. One night. If
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.31,0:47:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the air doesn't arrive, the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.21,0:47:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,clause stops mattering. My son
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.33,0:47:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.82,0:47:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,mine again. And the stranger
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.35,0:47:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,goes back to the street she came
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.10,0:47:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,from. The railing went ice cold
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.79,0:47:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,under my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.40,0:47:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The cerevaules she continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.36,0:47:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Already know about the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.85,0:47:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,pregnancy. I sent word
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.34,0:47:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.66,0:47:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Renolfo accepted the job for the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.47,0:47:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,price I offered. It won't be at
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.23,0:47:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the mansion. It'll be on the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.82,0:47:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,way out when she thinks she's
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.42,0:47:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,safe. And the three of you will
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.12,0:47:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,pretend you didn't know. And
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.66,0:47:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,after
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.94,0:47:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,word you'll pretend you're
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.22,0:47:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,sorry. And my son will pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.70,0:47:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for a month that he's lost
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.98,0:47:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,something
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.42,0:47:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,important. Then he'll go back to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.61,0:47:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,being what he was. Silence. The
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.72,0:47:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of silence three old men
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.71,0:47:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,make
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.98,0:47:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when none want to be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.68,0:47:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to speak. Then one of the elders
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.49,0:47:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,spoke. And this time I caught
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.13,0:47:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.30,0:47:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,whole sentence. It was Don
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.00,0:47:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sisto. The youngest of the three
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.08,0:47:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,old men. The one with the lowest
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.17,0:47:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.10,0:48:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an attempt against
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.56,0:48:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Caratiollo blood Otevia. This is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.35,0:48:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,an attempt against a bot
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.70,0:48:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,bride. She spat back without
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.83,0:48:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,pausing. Caratiollo blood is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.97,0:48:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,decided in this room. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.26,0:48:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,wait
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.56,0:48:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for the rest. I went down the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.31,0:48:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs far too slowly. Gripping
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.17,0:48:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the railing with both hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.32,0:48:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling the ice cold iron under
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.96,0:48:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,my fingers as if it were the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.45,0:48:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,only solid thing in that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.14,0:48:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,With the hand written draft warm
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.15,0:48:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in my pocket and my free hand
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.97,0:48:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,firm on my belly,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.68,0:48:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I crossed the service corridor,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.36,0:48:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,passed the winter garden without
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.09,0:48:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at the plants. All the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.72,0:48:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,way to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.04,0:48:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the back veranda. The one where
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.98,0:48:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd cried alone weeks before. On
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.98,0:48:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the day, Lutavico had told me
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.80,0:48:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the first
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.36,0:48:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,half of the truth. And I still
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.91,0:48:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't know there was a second
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.46,0:48:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,half. I leaned my hip against
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.96,0:48:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the stone
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.42,0:48:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,ballastrade. I breathed three
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.51,0:48:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,times. Deep, slow, counting the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.74,0:48:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds of each breath. The
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.68,0:48:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,doctor had
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.40,0:48:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,said on Monday's late afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.14,0:48:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that a big shock dropped the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.70,0:48:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,pressure and dropped pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.33,0:48:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.72,0:48:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the child. I wouldn't give the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.53,0:49:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,witch that satisfaction. I
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.11,0:49:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't run. I wouldn't scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.68,0:49:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I would tell Lutavico before
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.33,0:49:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Otevia made her next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.86,0:49:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Before Renolfo went out into the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.75,0:49:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,street
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.10,0:49:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with the agreed price in his
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.58,0:49:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,pocket. The clause had become a
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.22,0:49:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,small piece of her game. The big
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.92,0:49:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,piece
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.18,0:49:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,was me, alive, walking out the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.23,0:49:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,door. I couldn't let her move
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.22,0:49:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,first. I ran my hand over my
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.14,0:49:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,face.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.48,0:49:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was steady. Good. I turned to
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.87,0:49:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,go back into the house, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.04,0:49:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,saw. At the back wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.02,0:49:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,where the garden met the narrow
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.41,0:49:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,street that wrapped around the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.76,0:49:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,mansion, leaning against a stone
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.20,0:49:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,as if he'd been waiting since
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.93,0:49:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of the world. A
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.66,0:49:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,man, light gray suit. One hand
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.45,0:49:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.80,0:49:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The other arm loose and
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.39,0:49:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,unhurried. A shark's smile I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.46,0:49:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,seen once before. Months ago, in
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.67,0:49:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the street
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.36,0:49:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,behind the old market, when he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.28,0:49:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,gotten too close to Il Jira
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.90,0:49:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sole. And Lutavico had made him
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.76,0:49:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a treat with a look alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.68,0:49:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Renolfo Saravala. He raised his
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.97,0:49:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,free hand. Slowly. With that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.03,0:49:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,calm of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.14,0:49:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,who has all the time in the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.49,0:49:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,world and knows it. Like a man
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.99,0:50:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting an old acquaintance in
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.54,0:50:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.04,0:50:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of the street on a Sunday. He
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.68,0:50:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,held the gesture half a second
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.37,0:50:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in the air. His eyes fixed on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.01,0:50:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,mine
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.24,0:50:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,across the garden. Then he took
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.16,0:50:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,half a step back, entered the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.96,0:50:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,shadow of the wall, and
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.38,0:50:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.50,0:50:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood there with my hand on my
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.37,0:50:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,belly, without moving. Counting
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.18,0:50:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,my breath until I reached
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.64,0:50:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,10, the witch wasn't waiting for
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.81,0:50:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the next move. She'd already
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.71,0:50:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,made it. Chapter 5,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.24,0:50:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the night she chose to stay. The
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.31,0:50:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,blast entered my sleep before
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.19,0:50:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the sound itself did. It was a
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.13,0:50:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,dry
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.32,0:50:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,crack, far off at the back wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.42,0:50:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and then a second one closer
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.25,0:50:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,against the stone of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.62,0:50:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat up on the bed in the old
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.21,0:50:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,contract room with my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.59,0:50:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,already on my belly. As if my
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.14,0:50:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,body had
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.56,0:50:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,learned the gesture before I
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.16,0:50:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,did. The clock on the wall read
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.94,0:50:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,320 in the morning. I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.48,0:50:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,fastened in the corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.70,0:50:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,shouting orders at two men I
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.13,0:50:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't know. I heard footsteps
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.66,0:50:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,running
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.02,0:50:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,up the service stairs. I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.76,0:50:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Donakirah calling my name from
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.50,0:50:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere far off. My bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.19,0:50:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,door
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.42,0:50:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,opened with a shove. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.07,0:50:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,was there in the gap, wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.71,0:51:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,his coat over an open shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.82,0:51:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I recognized the coat before I
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.42,0:51:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,recognized his face. It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.06,0:51:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,same one from the rainy night,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.04,0:51:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,months ago. The same heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.47,0:51:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,fabric he'd put over my
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.74,0:51:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders without saying a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.50,0:51:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He never
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.94,0:51:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,knew I'd kept that detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.76,0:51:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither did I, until I saw it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.79,0:51:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,there again. Get up. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.54,0:51:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. I got up too fast. The
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.40,0:51:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,dizziness came at once. A wave
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.25,0:51:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of heat rising up my neck and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.05,0:51:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the room
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.54,0:51:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,spinning half a degree. He
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.77,0:51:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,caught me by the elbow before I
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.23,0:51:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,could hit the corner of the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.50,0:51:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,nightstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.62,0:51:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly, he repeated, lower. We
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.99,0:51:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,went down. In the hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.81,0:51:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Donakirah was crouched behind
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.11,0:51:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the sofa
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.74,0:51:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,with Narina, who'd shown up at
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.43,0:51:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the mansion without my knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.13,0:51:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when. Bastion was at the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.34,0:51:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun in hand. His face without a
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.26,0:51:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,single line more than usual. One
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.23,0:51:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of the pains in the formal
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.84,0:51:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting room had shattered on
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.33,0:51:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the floor in long shards. One of
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.98,0:51:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,them caught my arm when I passed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.62,0:51:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,too close. The cut was a graze.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.03,0:51:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Short. More shock than blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.28,0:51:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ludovico saw the red line
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.22,0:52:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,rise on my white skin before I
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.48,0:52:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,felt it. We're leaving here. He
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.81,0:52:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,said, now. Bastion drove. I sat
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.15,0:52:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.60,0:52:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,exit with Ludovico holding a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.20,0:52:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,folded cloth against my forearm.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.03,0:52:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He pressed with the firmness of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.80,0:52:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.86,0:52:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,man who'd done this more times
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.44,0:52:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,than any man should. The lights
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.08,0:52:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of Providence passed by the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.50,0:52:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,window
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.82,0:52:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in yellow smears. No one spoke
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.68,0:52:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,for three kilometers. I had a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.47,0:52:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,secret that could no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.14,0:52:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,sleep in my
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.82,0:52:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,pocket. Ludovico. He turned his
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.63,0:52:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,face toward me without letting
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.39,0:52:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,go of the cloth. I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.58,0:52:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, and your mother has
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.11,0:52:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,already sold that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.80,0:52:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He closed his eyes for half a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.44,0:52:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,second.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.84,0:52:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all. No start. No
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.98,0:52:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,shout. No idiotic question. When
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.62,0:52:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,he opened his eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.48,0:52:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,they were those of the man the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.05,0:52:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,city feared. But turned only
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.51,0:52:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the inside of the car. I
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.13,0:52:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,know
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.34,0:52:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,what to do. Bastion took a
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.93,0:52:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,narrow road climbing into the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.71,0:52:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,hills. I vaguely recognized the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.61,0:52:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.48,0:52:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Without knowing why. Ludovico
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.28,0:52:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't tell me where we were
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.01,0:52:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,going. Nor did I ask. The house
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.93,0:52:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,was at
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.30,0:52:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of a packed dirt path
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.38,0:53:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,surrounded by tall pines. Dark
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.53,0:53:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,stone facade. Windows shut for
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.68,0:53:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,years. Tiles covered in dry
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.37,0:53:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,needles. Bastion stopped the car
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.37,0:53:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,near the entrance and got out
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.18,0:53:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,first.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.06,0:53:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He stood at the door. Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.64,0:53:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,resting on his thigh. His eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.53,0:53:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,on the road we'd come by. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.55,0:53:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.68,0:53:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,father's. Ludovico said, opening
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.71,0:53:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the door for me. No one here was
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.74,0:53:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ever happy. But no one knows
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.52,0:53:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of this house outside of three
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.40,0:53:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,people. I went in. The smell of
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.34,0:53:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,shut up wood. Dust from more
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.10,0:53:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,than one
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.60,0:53:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,winter. A distant trace of dried
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.44,0:53:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,lavender in some piece of
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.88,0:53:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,furniture. You lit the hearth
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.55,0:53:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,without yet
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.18,0:53:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,taking off his coat. The fire
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.04,0:53:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,caught fast. Hungry for the old
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.03,0:53:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,paper he stacked beneath the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.82,0:53:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,kindling. He knelt with me
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.40,0:53:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,before the hearth. A thick rug
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.23,0:53:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,cushioning our knees. From the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.06,0:53:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,small
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.36,0:53:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,kit Bastion had thrown into the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.40,0:53:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,car. He took a clean bandage, a
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.45,0:53:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,dark bottle, and cotton. It'll
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.42,0:53:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,sting.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.38,0:53:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, I've had worse sting.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.51,0:53:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He almost laughed. He didn't. He
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.79,0:53:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,ran the antiseptic over my arm
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.92,0:53:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,with the patience of a man who'd
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.88,0:54:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,been taught to kill and was
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.53,0:54:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,learning, right there, to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.88,0:54:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand paused a second longer
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.78,0:54:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,than it needed to over the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.73,0:54:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A small second. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.82,0:54:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My chest registered it as if it
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.72,0:54:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,were a whole minute. I almost
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.50,0:54:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,believed it. I said, looking at
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.41,0:54:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.52,0:54:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,These two days. I almost
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.89,0:54:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,believed you'd planned it all to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.71,0:54:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,lose me. He didn't stop the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.24,0:54:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.26,0:54:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He just answered in the same low
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.01,0:54:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,tone. I planned to lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.50,0:54:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because I didn't know I could
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.09,0:54:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.36,0:54:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence after that was
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.02,0:54:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,thick. The hearth crackled.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.75,0:54:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside the wind passed through
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.73,0:54:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.92,0:54:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,pines with a sound like
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.11,0:54:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing. He wrapped the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.39,0:54:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,bandage around my arm with a
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.84,0:54:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,firm not on one side.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.50,0:54:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There. He said. I didn't stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.64,0:54:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither did he. He lifted his
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.65,0:54:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,hand from my elbow to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.08,0:54:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly, giving me time to pull
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.92,0:54:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,back if I wanted. I didn't pull
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.82,0:54:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,back. His thumb stopped on my
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.59,0:54:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.22,0:54:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I leaned my forehead against
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.62,0:54:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,his. It was the gesture we'd
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.01,0:54:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,invented in the bedroom corridor
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.61,0:54:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.16,0:54:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I'd kept is if it were a
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.47,0:54:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,password only hours. If I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.70,0:55:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.72,0:55:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you murmured. It's like
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.33,0:55:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,choosing. Again, good. He kissed
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.56,0:55:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,me as if he were apologizing and
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.80,0:55:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,promising at
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.64,0:55:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the same time. It wasn't the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.28,0:55:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,kiss of a man who thinks he's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.97,0:55:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,one. It was the kiss of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.67,0:55:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.96,0:55:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,finally stopped losing on
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.43,0:55:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,purpose. The heat of the hearth
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.25,0:55:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,struck my back. The fabric of
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.95,0:55:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,his coat was
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.66,0:55:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,rough beneath my fingers. I
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.14,0:55:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,smelled the fire, the antiseptic
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.91,0:55:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,him. I thought in a flash too
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.50,0:55:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,quick to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.94,0:55:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,hold that I'd waited weeks to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.67,0:55:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,breathe this close again. I
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.28,0:55:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,thought I was still afraid. I
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.00,0:55:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,thought the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.66,0:55:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,fear now was of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.49,0:55:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He laid me down on the rug
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.02,0:55:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly. He slid his arm under
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.72,0:55:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.90,0:55:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,nape of my neck. Before letting
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.71,0:55:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,my weight rest on the floor. As
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.51,0:55:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,if my body were the most
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.91,0:55:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,delicate
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.38,0:55:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,thing he'd ever carried. His
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.24,0:55:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,hand moved down the side of my
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.24,0:55:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,hip and stopped. Open. Over the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.31,0:55:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,still
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.64,0:55:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,invisible curve of my belly. It
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.34,0:55:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed there. He looked at my
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.92,0:55:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,belly like a man looking at a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.51,0:55:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,secret
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.84,0:55:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that had become a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.90,0:55:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hours. He said, low, my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.12,0:55:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,stung. I didn't let them fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.50,0:55:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.50,0:55:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.52,0:56:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And my voice came out firmer
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.04,0:56:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,than I expected. In yours, he
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.61,0:56:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled the coat off his
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.86,0:56:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.06,0:56:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,took off his shirt, and stood
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.44,0:56:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,there in the orange light of the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.97,0:56:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,hearth with the old marks of his
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.49,0:56:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,life
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.68,0:56:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,on display. A long scar on his
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.64,0:56:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,left shoulder, a smaller one
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.47,0:56:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,near his ribs. The outline of a
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.49,0:56:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,small
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.82,0:56:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,tattoo on his chest I'd never
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.38,0:56:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,seen up close. I touched each of
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.11,0:56:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,them with my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.94,0:56:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly. Like someone reading a
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.03,0:56:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,story in Braille. He closed his
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.19,0:56:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes. You tremble when I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.28,0:56:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.78,0:56:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, only you. I pulled his
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.13,0:56:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,face to mine. This time the kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.64,0:56:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,was deeper, slower, with a kind
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.06,0:56:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.22,0:56:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,hunger and no hurry at all. His
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.01,0:56:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,weight on my chest was dense and
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.86,0:56:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,alive. The rug beneath my back
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.60,0:56:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,was rough
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.12,0:56:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and just the right measure. He
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.53,0:56:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,undid the strap of my night gown
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.03,0:56:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,with a patience that almost
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.30,0:56:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,irritated
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.72,0:56:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,me. Slighting the thin fabric
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.36,0:56:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,off my shoulders until it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.78,0:56:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,exposed my breasts to the heat
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.48,0:56:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.82,0:56:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,earth. His large hands cupped
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.51,0:56:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,each of them with reverence. His
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.38,0:56:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,thumbs tracing slow circles
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.95,0:56:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,around
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.30,0:56:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the nipples that hardened under
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.80,0:57:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,his touch, pressing with enough
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.30,0:57:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,delicacy to draw a trembling
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.66,0:57:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,sigh from my lips. Ludovico.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.12,0:57:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly. He answered, his mouth
